{{阿富汗政治}}
'''2014年阿富汗总统选举'''在2014年4月5日举行<ref>{{cite web|author=|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-20145147|title=Afghanistan presidential vote date is announced|publisher=BBC News|date=30 October 2012|accessdate=3 February 2014|archive-date=2018-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211123419/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-20145147|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现任[[阿富汗总统|总统]][[哈米德·卡尔扎伊|哈米德·卡尔扎伊]]已连任两届，根据阿法律，卡尔扎伊不能参加此次竞选。2013年9月16日至10月6日开始登记总统选举候选人资格，<ref name=khaama>{{cite web|url=http://www.khaama.com/dr-zalmai-rasoul-nominated-for-2014-presidential-elections-1940|title=Dr. Zalmai Rasoul nominated for 2014 presidential elections|publisher=|date=6 October 2013|accessdate=3 February 2014|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003171823/https://www.khaama.com/dr-zalmai-rasoul-nominated-for-2014-presidential-elections-1940/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此次共有27名候选人参加选举。<ref name=fp>{{cite web|author=Bailey Cahall|url=http://afpak.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2013/10/07/27_individuals_submit_nomination_papers_for_afghanistans_2014_presidential_election|title=27 candidates enter race for Afghanistan's 2014 presidential election|publisher=[[Foreign_Policy_(magazine)|Foreign Policy]]|date=7 October 2013|accessdate=3 February 2014|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029192457/http://afpak.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2013/10/07/27_individuals_submit_nomination_papers_for_afghanistans_2014_presidential_election|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，在10月22日阿富汗独立选举委员会剔除其中16名候选人资格，而剩下11人竞选。<ref name=aljazeera>{{cite web|author=Ali M Latifi|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/10/sixteen-afghan-election-hopefuls-disqualified-2013102213563537306.html|title=Sixteen Afghan election hopefuls disqualified|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=22 October 2013|accessdate=3 February 2014|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409214338/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/10/sixteen-afghan-election-hopefuls-disqualified-2013102213563537306.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>观察家认为，主要的竞争在两位前外长——[[阿卜杜拉·阿卜杜拉|阿卜杜拉·阿卜杜拉]]和[[扎尔迈·拉苏尔|扎尔迈·拉苏尔]]以及前财政部长[[阿什拉夫·加尼|阿什拉夫·加尼]]之间展开。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/29/world/asia/polling-comes-to-afghanistan-suggesting-limit-to-sway-of-president-karzai.html|title=Polling Comes to Afghanistan, Suggesting Limit to Sway of President Karzai|publisher=NewYorkTimes|date=28 December 2013|accessdate=7 February 2014|archive-date=2019-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505025932/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/29/world/asia/polling-comes-to-afghanistan-suggesting-limit-to-sway-of-president-karzai.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本次选举是阿富汗历史上首次民主权力交接。<ref>{{cite news|title=Huge security as Afghan presidential election looms|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26880022|newspaper=BBC|date=April 4, 2014|accessdate=2014-04-07|archive-date=2018-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111170452/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26880022|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Afghanistan votes in historic presidential election|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26893972|newspaper=BBC|date=5 April 2014|accessdate=2014-04-07|archive-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724113932/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26893972|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Shalizi and Harooni|first=Hamid and Mirwais|title=Landmark Afghanistan Presidential Election Held Under Shadow of Violence|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/04/landmark-afghan-election-_n_5095143.html|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=April 4, 2014|accessdate=2014-04-07|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225603/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/04/landmark-afghan-election-_n_5095143.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Afghanistan's Future: Who's Who in Pivotal Presidential Election|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/afghanistans-future-whos-who-pivotal-presidential-election-n24756|newspaper=NBC News|accessdate=2014-04-07|archive-date=2018-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802232817/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/afghanistans-future-whos-who-pivotal-presidential-election-n24756|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
2013年7月17日，[[阿富汗议会|阿富汗议会]]正式通过新选举法。此选举法共16章80款。7月20日，总统卡尔扎伊签署新选举法案。法案的签署为2014年4月5日大选如期举行提供了法律保障。<ref>{{cite news|last=Rosenburg|first=Matthew|title=With New Law, Afghanistan Moves Closer to an Election|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/18/world/asia/with-new-law-afghanistan-moves-closer-to-an-election.html?ref=global-home|accessdate=3 February 2014|newspaper=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|date=17 July 2013|archive-date=2013-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113085830/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/18/world/asia/with-new-law-afghanistan-moves-closer-to-an-election.html?ref=global-home|dead-url=no}}</ref>

